2) You cannot complete the quest until you are over 50, but usually 55 is the average level now for completing it provided your guild can kill Venril and you can reserve Fear for the Broken Golem. If your guild can't do either of these you may ask if you can join another raid killing in Fear for the golem, and maybe tag along with a guild killing VS for legs that doesn't need the Gnarled staff any more. Phinigel is killable by 1 group, so you shouldn't have much problem killing him. Don't expect the staff ont he first try though, his drop rate is significantly less than other epic quest MOBs.<br>
